    yardstick
NeedsCompilation: yes
ByteCompile: true
SystemRequirements: Dedicated Linux/HPC host recommended: Intel Xeon Platinum 8260-class CPU, high-memory NUMA server, LightGBM and XGBoost runtimes. Optional external Limbo ask/tell executable configured via TBTB_LIMBO_COMMAND.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
